  "version": "0.1",
  "description": "Heuristic fabric ontology: expected tactile/thermal properties per fiber, adjectives that signal the claimed fiber is NOT what the customer received, and the cheap fiber it is most often substituted with. substitution_signature = the tactile tells a fiber leaves when masquerading as another (used by the diagnosis engine to corroborate substitution hypotheses).",
